<L>Snapp'd with illumin'd hands each flaming &s;haft,</L>
<L>His tingling fingers &s;hook, and &s;tamp'd, and laugh'd;</L>
<L><PB N="39" REF="49">Bright o'er the floor the &s;catter'd fragments blaz'd,<MILESTONE N="395"></L>
<L>And Gods retreating trembled as they gaz'd;</L>
<L>The immortal Sire, indulgent to his child,</L>
<L>Bow'd his ambro&s;ial locks, and Heaven relenting &s;miled.</L>
