<L>III. "Where with chill frown enormous ALPS alarms</L>
<L>A thou&s;and realms, horizon'd in his arms;</L>
<L>While cloudle&s;s &s;uns meridian glories &s;hed <MILESTONE N="105"></L>
<L>From &s;kies of &s;ilver round his hoary head,</L>
