<L>And purpled mead,&mdash;her&s;elf a fairer flower;</L>
<L>Sudden, un&s;een amid the twilight glade,</L>
<L>Ru&s;h'd gloomy DIS, and &s;eized the trembling maid.&mdash;</L>
