<L>Dropp'd from their gauzy laps the gather'd &s;weets,</L>
<L>Clung round the &s;truggling Nymph, with piercing cries,</L>
<L>Pur&s;ued the chariot, and invoked the &s;kies;&mdash;</L>
<L>Plea&s;ed as he gra&s;ps her in his iron arms,</L>
<L>Frights with &s;oft &s;ighs, with tender words alarms,<MILESTONE N="190"></L>
