<L>Part his blue plains, and people all his rocks.</L>
<L><PB N="179" REF="190">Deep, in warm waves beneath the Line that roll,<MILESTONE N="205"></L>
<L>Beneath the &s;hadowy ice-i&s;les of the Pole,</L>
<L>Onward, through bright meandering vales, afar,</L>
<L>Obedient Sharks &s;hall trail her &s;ceptred car,</L>
<L>With harne&s;s'd necks the pearly flood di&s;turb,</L>
<L>Stretch the &s;ilk rein, and champ the &s;ilver curb; <MILESTONE N="210"></L>
<L>Plea&s;ed round her triumph wondering Tritons play,</L>
