<L>The &s;moother Rind its &s;oft embroidery &s;pread</L>
<L>In vaulted <HI>Petals</HI> o'er their fertile bed;</L>
<L>While the rough Bark, in circling mazes roll'd,</L>
<L>Forms the green <HI>Cup</HI> with many a wrinkled fold;</L>
<L>And each &s;mall bud-&s;cale &s;preads its foliage hard,<MILESTONE N="475"></L>
<L>Firm round the callow germ, a <HI>Floral Guard.</HI></L>
