</DIV2>
<DIV2 N="23" TYPE="note">
<HEAD>NOTE XXIII.....COAL.</HEAD>
<P>1. A fountain of fo&s;&s;ile tar in Shrop&s;hire; has been di&s;tilled from the coal-beds
