</DIV2>
<DIV2 N="24" TYPE="note">
<HEAD>NOTE XXIV.....GRANITE.</HEAD>
<P>GRANITE the lowe&s;t &s;tratum of the earth yet known; porphory, trap, Moor-&s;tone,
