<L><PB N="89" REF="470">From realm to realm, with cro&s;s or cre&s;cent crown'd,</L>
<L>Where'er Mankind and Mi&s;ery are found,</L>
<L>O'er burning &s;ands, deep waves, or wilds of &s;now,<MILESTONE N="445"></L>
