<L>De&s;cending Sylphs relax the trembling &s;trings,<MILESTONE N="475"></L>
<L>And catch the rain-drops on their &s;hadowy wings.</L>
<L>&mdash;And now her va&s;e a mode&s;t Naiad fills</L>
