<L>And Silence drove their ebon cars along; <MILESTONE N="390"></L>
<L>Six lovely daughters, and their father, &s;wept</L>
<L>To the throng'd grave CLEONE &s;aw, and wept;</L>
<L><PB N="127" REF="508">Her tender mind, with meek Religion fraught,</L>
<L>Drank all-re&s;igned Affliction's bitter draught;</L>
<L>Alive and li&s;tening to the whi&s;per'd groan <MILESTONE N="395"></L>
