<L>Where MUNDY pour'd, the li&s;tening nymphs among,<NOTE PLACE="foot"><P><HI>Where Mundy.</HI> l. 35. Alluding to an unpublished poem by F. N. Mundy, E&s;q. on his leaving Needwood-Fore&s;t.</P></NOTE><MILESTONE N="35"></L>
